La Collection Privée presents its luxurious assortment of couture caps, inspired by the legacy of Christian Dior, visionary couturier-perfumer, to adorn its fragrances with the iconic motifs of the House. They celebrate the union between the olfactory elegance of La Collection Privée and the couture know-how of the House of Dior.
 
*Available for 100ml and 200ml formats.
